    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896760/extras/336d84337690cf87c0083b42f8091128.poster.avif?t=1771934904\" width=600 height=70 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896760/extras/336d84337690cf87c0083b42f8091128.webm?t=1771934904\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>《Underling Uprising》采用了“清版动作游戏”玩法，并融合了怀旧的 90 年代卡通片创意灵感。在全球范围内进行战斗，他们是一群经过科技增强的实验体，每个人都拥有独特的能力。你只有一个任务：制止那个创造你的疯狂科学家！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896760/extras/f45fe9ca16f147b78ab87c1b35142b5d.poster.avif?t=1771934904\" width=600 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896760/extras/f45fe9ca16f147b78ab87c1b35142b5d.webm?t=1771934904\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>即兴创造新的连招，以击败互动要素丰富且颇具挑战性的敌人。尝试开放式的连招系统，每种连招都有着很大的优化空间！一旦你积攒了足够的能量，就可以释放强大且炫目的超级必杀技！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896760/extras/c2f8ad63372392c0c17fbd205181e6d9.poster.avif?t=1771934904\" width=600 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896760/extras/c2f8ad63372392c0c17fbd205181e6d9.webm?t=1771934904\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>操控各种强大的载具来痛击你的敌人！这些载具将包括太空舱、机甲等等！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896760/extras/9e35c8bf880aaffb4b4773fa7566ffb4.poster.avif?t=1771934904\" width=600 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896760/extras/9e35c8bf880aaffb4b4773fa7566ffb4.webm?t=1771934904\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>学习每个角色的大量招式，包括超级护甲、悬浮、动画取消和双跳等机制！每个游戏周目都将是一次独一无二的体验，并可以不断精益求精！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896760/extras/8bb7be322bdf43d8244a008ca689871b.poster.avif?t=1771934904\" width=600 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896760/extras/8bb7be322bdf43d8244a008ca689871b.webm?t=1771934904\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>在复仇的征途中，你将遭遇各种挡路的头目和小头目，你必须施展出浑身解数，以图克敌制胜！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最多支持 4 名玩家的本地合作模式和对战模式！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索横跨世界（甚至更远）的 7 个长关卡！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为寻求更多挑战的玩家准备了多种难度选项！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在街机模式中突破自己的最高分！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拾取各种临时武器来提升战斗爽快感！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >简单易记的控制方案！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所有角色均可奔跑，所以你永远不会感到慢！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896760/extras/c6f003f284502d46810faa9d5e49627d.poster.avif?t=1771934904\" width=600 height=70 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896760/extras/c6f003f284502d46810faa9d5e49627d.webm?t=1771934904\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
